title: (Fr) Access to other federal, provincial or territorial dental benefits
main-content:
(Fr) Access to dental coverage through a provincial, territorial or federal government social program will not impact your eligibility for the Canadian Dental Care Plan.

If you meet all the eligibility criteria, your coverage will be coordinated between the plans to ensure there are no duplication or gaps in coverage.

federal-benefit.title: (Fr) Federal benefits
federal-benefit.legend: (Fr) Do you have dental benefits through a social program offered by a federal program?

provincial-territorial.title: (Fr) Provincial or territorial benefits
provincial-territorial.legend: (Fr) Do you have dental benefits through a social program offered by your province or territory?
provincial-territorial.option-yes: (Fr) Yes, I have provincial or territorial benefits.
provincial-territorial.option-no: (Fr) I do not have provincial or territorial benefits.
